189        /**
190         * Create a builder for {@code io.jstach.rainbowgum.rabbitmq.RabbitMQOutput }.
191         * @param name will fill <code>{name}</code> in <code>logging.output.{name}.</code>. Used to resolve config and give the output a name.
192         */
193        public RabbitMQOutputBuilder(
194                        java.lang.String name
195                        ) {
196                java.util.Map<String,String> prefixParameters = java.util.Map.of(
197                                "name", name
198                        );
199                this.propertyPrefix = LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_PREFIX, prefixParameters);
200                this.name = name;
201                property_uri = Property.builder()
202                        .toURI()
203                        .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_uri, prefixParameters));
204
205                property_exchange = Property.builder()
206                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_exchange, prefixParameters));
207
208                property_routingKey = Property.builder()
209                        .map(_v -> io.jstach.rainbowgum.rabbitmq.RabbitMQOutput.toRoutingKeyFunction(_v))
210                        .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_routingKey, prefixParameters));
211
212                property_declareExchange = Property.builder()
213                        .toBoolean()
214                        .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_declareExchange, prefixParameters));
215
216                property_host = Property.builder()
217                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_host, prefixParameters));
218
219                property_username = Property.builder()
220                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_username, prefixParameters));
221
222                property_password = Property.builder()
223                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_password, prefixParameters));
224
225                property_port = Property.builder()
226                        .toInt()
227                        .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_port, prefixParameters));
228
229                property_appId = Property.builder()
230                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_appId, prefixParameters));
231
232                property_connectionName = Property.builder()
233                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_connectionName, prefixParameters));
234
235                property_exchangeType = Property.builder()
236                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_exchangeType, prefixParameters));
237
238                property_virtualHost = Property.builder()
239                                                .build(LogProperties.interpolateKey(PROPERTY_virtualHost, prefixParameters));
240
241        }

410        /**
411         * Fills the builder from properties.
412         * @param properties not null.
413         * @return this updated builder.
414         */
415        public RabbitMQOutputBuilder fromProperties(LogProperties properties) {
416                this.uri = property_uri.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.uri);
417                this.exchange = property_exchange.get(properties).value(this.exchange);
418                this.routingKey = property_routingKey.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.routingKey);
419                this.declareExchange = property_declareExchange.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.declareExchange);
420                this.host = property_host.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.host);
421                this.username = property_username.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.username);
422                this.password = property_password.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.password);
423                this.port = property_port.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.port);
424                this.appId = property_appId.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.appId);
425                this.connectionName = property_connectionName.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.connectionName);
426                this.exchangeType = property_exchangeType.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.exchangeType);
427                this.virtualHost = property_virtualHost.get(properties).valueOrNull(this.virtualHost);
428                return this;
429        }

431        /**
432         * Turns the builder into java.util.Properties like Map skipping values that are null.
433         * @param consumer apply is called where first arg is key and second is value.
434         */
435        public void toProperties(java.util.function.BiConsumer<String, String> consumer) {
436                if (this.uri != null) {
437                        consumer.accept(property_uri.key(), property_uri.propertyString(this.uri));
438                }
439                if (this.exchange != null) {
440                        consumer.accept(property_exchange.key(), property_exchange.propertyString(this.exchange));
441                }
442                if (this.routingKey != null) {
443                        consumer.accept(property_routingKey.key(), property_routingKey.propertyString(this.routingKey));
444                }
445                if (this.declareExchange != null) {
446                        consumer.accept(property_declareExchange.key(), property_declareExchange.propertyString(this.declareExchange));
447                }
448                if (this.host != null) {
449                        consumer.accept(property_host.key(), property_host.propertyString(this.host));
450                }
451                if (this.username != null) {
452                        consumer.accept(property_username.key(), property_username.propertyString(this.username));
453                }
454                if (this.password != null) {
455                        consumer.accept(property_password.key(), property_password.propertyString(this.password));
456                }
457                if (this.port != null) {
458                        consumer.accept(property_port.key(), property_port.propertyString(this.port));
459                }
460                if (this.appId != null) {
461                        consumer.accept(property_appId.key(), property_appId.propertyString(this.appId));
462                }
463                if (this.connectionName != null) {
464                        consumer.accept(property_connectionName.key(), property_connectionName.propertyString(this.connectionName));
465                }
466                if (this.exchangeType != null) {
467                        consumer.accept(property_exchangeType.key(), property_exchangeType.propertyString(this.exchangeType));
468                }
469                if (this.virtualHost != null) {
470                        consumer.accept(property_virtualHost.key(), property_virtualHost.propertyString(this.virtualHost));
471                }
472        }
